AnatoLaks is a music band based in Oslo, mainly covering songs in the genres of Turkish Rock and Anatolian Rock (a fusion of Turkish folk music and rock).

The band was founded in 2024 by Arda Ünlüsoy (drums), Burak Kara (vocalist, electric guitar) and Yavuzer Çetin (electric guitar). And finally, Numan Hekimoğlu joined as the bassist, completed the lineup. Each member is an experienced musician who has previously performed at various well-known events in Türkiye. These four individuals, each with different backgrounds, came together in Oslo and now share a common goal: To carry the unique sound of Anatolia beyond borders!
